Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.39,0:03:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,听好 你的性命可能全靠这个了\N{\fs13}DOCTOR: Listen, your life could depend on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别眨眼 一下都不能眨 一眨眼你就会死\N{\fs13}Don't blink. Don't even blink. Blink and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.53,0:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它们很快 比你想像的要快\N{\fs13}They are fast. Faster than you can believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,别转身 别回头 千万别眨眼\N{\fs13}Don't turn your back, don't look away and don't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs13}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs13}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,受了点惊吓 想聊聊 帮你煮咖啡呢\N{\fs13}Bit freaked. Need to talk. Making you a coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.11,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽·斯帕罗 现在是凌晨一点\N{\fs13}Sally Sparrow, it's 1:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.32,0:04:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你认为我会在凌晨一点出门吗\N{\fs13}Do you think I'm going out at 1:00 in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.88,0:04:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我在厨房\N{\fs13}I'm in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.84,0:04:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你客厅那些屏幕是怎么回事\N{\fs13}What's that on all those screens in your front room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 老天\N{\fs13}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 老天 莎丽\N{\fs13}Oh, God. Sally,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你还没遇到我哥哥拉瑞吧\N{\fs13}you've met my brother Larry, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你会的\N{\fs13}You 're about to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.63,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\N{\fs13}Not sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.47,0:04:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但真的 真的希望…\N{\fs13}but really, really hoping…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.84,0:04:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我穿着裤子吗\N{\fs13}Pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.30,0:04:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,快穿上\N{\fs13}Put them on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.11,0:04:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,快穿上 我恨你\N{\fs13}Put them on! I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想什么\N{\fs13}What are you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我的蠢蛋哥哥\N{\fs13}My useless brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 怎么了\N{\fs13}Sally? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.37,0:04:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,发生了什么\N{\fs13}What's happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnSimHei\fs20\1c&0000DD\3c&FCFCFD\bord2\an3}危险区域\N禁止入内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 开始调查吧\N{\fs13}Okay. Let's investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.00,0:05:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我 女子侦查队\N{\fs13}You and me, girl investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.89,0:05:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢\N{\fs13}Love it. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 "麻雀和夜莺"\N{\fs13}Hey! Sparrow and Nightingale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,太合拍了\N{\fs13}That so works.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.38,0:05:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,像ITV侦探剧似的\N{\fs13}Bit ITV.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fs13}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 你上次来这里干嘛\N{\fs13}What did you come here for anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.31,0:05:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢古老的东西\N{\fs13}I love old things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,它们使我伤感\N{\fs13}They make me feel sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,伤感有什么好的\N{\fs13}What's good about sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,对深沉的人来说就是快乐\N{\fs13}It's happy for deep people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,哭泣天使\N{\fs13} The weeping angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我的花园里可不会放这个\N{\fs13}KATHY: Wouldn't have that in my garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,它动过了\N{\fs13}It's moved
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它怎么了\N{\fs13}It's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.26,0:05:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,跟昨晚比\N{\fs13}Since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我确定 它更近了\N{\fs13}I'm sure of it. It's closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.92,0:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,它离房子更近了\N{\fs13}It's got closer to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我的名字怎么会被写在这里\N{\fs13}How can my name be written here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能\N{\fs13}How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会来这里\N{\fs13}Who'd come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 可能是小偷\N{\fs13}What are you doing? It could be a burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小偷会摇门铃吗\N{\fs13}A burglar who rings the doorbell?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我留在这里以防…\N{\fs13}Okay. I'll stay here in case of…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,以防什么\N{\fs13}In case of?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以防万一\N{\fs13}Incidents?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我在找莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}I'm looking for Sally Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道我会在这里\N{\fs13}How did you know I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有人委托我把这封信带来\N{\fs13}I was told to bring this letter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.80,0:07:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,在今天 这个确切的时刻\N{\fs13}on this date at this exact time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.84,0:07:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,送给莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}to Sally Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很旧\N{\fs13}Looks old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,本来就很旧\N{\fs13}It is old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.39,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思\N{\fs13}I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你身上有没有带着照片\N{\fs13}do you have anything with a photograph on it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,比如驾照之类的\N{\fs13}like a driving license?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么有人知道我会来 我没告诉过任何人\N{\fs13}No one knew I was coming here. I didn't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能有人知道\N{\fs13}How could anyone have known?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这有点复杂\N{\fs13}MAN: It's all a bit complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不确定自己是否理解\N{\fs13}I'm not sure I understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.74,0:07:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 这可能有点傻\N{\fs13}Sorry, I feel really stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但委托人说必须完全确认\N{\fs13}I was told to make absolutely sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这么小的照片挺难分辨的 对吧\N{\fs13}It's so hard to tell with these little photographs, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.84,0:07:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,很显然\N{\fs13}Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs13}Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得应该没错\N{\fs13}here goes, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.69,0:07:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉真奇怪 过了这么多年\N{\fs13}Funny feeling after all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.44,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁寄来的\N{\fs13}Who's it from?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那是个很长的故事\N{\fs13}Well, that's a long story, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我名字\N{\fs13}Give me a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳·温赖特\N{\fs13}Katherine Wainwright
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但她特别嘱咐我告诉你\N{\fs13}But she specified I should tell you that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,在她结婚前\N{\fs13}prior to marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.77,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020\shad0.6}[英文的"南丁格尔" 即 "夜莺"]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.78,0:08:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她叫做凯茜·南丁格尔\N{\fs13}she was called Kathy Nightingale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜 没错\N{\fs13}Kathy. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳·凯斯特洛·南丁格尔\N{\fs13}Katherine Costello Nightingale
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个玩笑吗\N{\fs13}Is this a joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,玩笑\N{\fs13}Joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜 是你搞的吗\N{\fs13}Kathy, is this you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,很好笑\N{\fs13}Very funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.01,0:08:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜 凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy? Kathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你\N{\fs13}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,请一定要收下这个\N{\fs13}You need to take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应过她的\N{\fs13}I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fs13}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哪里\N{\fs13}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.66,0:09:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚在伦敦\N{\fs13}I was in London.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚刚在伦敦市中心\N{\fs13}I was in the middle of London.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.32,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在赫尔\N{\fs13}You're in Hull
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.07,0:09:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在\N{\fs13}No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.33,0:09:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是赫尔\N{\fs13}This is Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.37,0:09:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是\N{\fs13}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.91,0:09:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你在赫尔\N{\fs13}You're in Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.00,0:09:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在赫尔 别再说赫尔了\N{\fs13}I'm not in Hull. Stop saying Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs13}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么在这里\N{\fs13}Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我答应过她\N{\fs13}I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,答应过谁\N{\fs13}Who to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖母\N{\fs13}My grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑟琳·凯斯特洛·南丁格尔\N{\fs13}Katherine Costello Nightingale.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,伦敦可没这个 这上面没有叫这个的\N{\fs13}Don't have that in London. There's no call for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,都是赫尔\N{\fs13}It's all Hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,1920年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你的祖母\N{\fs13}Your grandmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,她20年前就去世了\N{\fs13}She died 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哼\N{\fs13}Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,难道她们是亲戚\N{\fs13}So they're related?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}Sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.68,0:09:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的凯茜和你的祖母\N{\fs13}My Kathy, your grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她们长得一模一样\N{\fs13}They're practically identical.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪里\N{\fs13}Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我亲爱的莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}My dearest Sally Sparrow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我的孙子履行了他的承诺\N{\fs13}if my grandson has done as he promises he will
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.71,0:10:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那么你读到这封信时\N{\fs13}then as you read these words
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对你来说 几分钟前我们才说过话\N{\fs13}it has been mere minutes since we last spoke,for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 已经过了60多年\N{\fs13}For me, it has been over 60 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.32,0:10:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,第三张照片是我的孩子们\N{\fs13}The third of the photographs is of my children.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,最小的叫做莎丽\N{\fs13}The youngest is Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 是按照你的名字起的\N{\fs13}I named her after you, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这太过分了\N{\fs13}This is sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,实在太过分了\N{\fs13}This is totally sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.30,0:10:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,凯茜\N{\fs13}Kathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不 别走 等等\N{\fs13}No, wait. Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜 除非我能非常长寿\N{\fs13}I suppose, unless I live to a really exceptional old age
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,否则你读到这信时我一定早已去世\N{\fs13}I will be long gone as you read this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.01,0:12:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,别为我难过\N{\fs13}Don't feel sorry for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.90,0:12:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我过的很幸福很充实\N{\fs13}I have lea' a good and full life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.03,0:12:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱上了一个好人\N{\fs13}I've loved a good man
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,也受到了他的真心对待\N{\fs13}and been well loved in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你会喜欢本的\N{\fs13}You would have liked Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.93,0:12:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我在1920年遇到的第一个人\N{\fs13}He was the very first person I met in 1920.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.64,0:12:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在跟踪我吗\N{\fs13}Are you following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你能别跟着我了吗\N{\fs13}Are you going to stop following me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.87,0:12:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我想不会\N{\fs13}No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.26,0:13:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,才在2007年吸了一口气\N{\fs13}To take one breath in 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.00,0:13:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,又在1920年呼出来\N{\fs13}and the next in 1920
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真是一种奇特的开始新生活的方式\N{\fs13}is a strange way to start a new life
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.66,0:13:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但新生活正是我一直想要的\N{\fs13}but a new life is exactly what I've always wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.33,0:13:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,1902
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.42,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你骗他你18岁 你这个小骗子\N{\fs13}You told him you were 18, you lying cow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你那个时候我父母已经去世\N{\fs13}My mum and dad are gone by your time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只能跟劳伦斯说了\N{\fs13}so really there's only Lawrence to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,他在女王大街的DVD商店工作\N{\fs13}He works at the DVD store on Queen Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.65,0:13:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你要怎么跟他说\N{\fs13}I don't know what you're gonna say to him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道你会想到办法的\N{\fs13}but I know you'll think of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉他我爱他\N{\fs13}just tell him I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了 我找劳伦斯·南丁格尔\N{\fs13}Excuse me. I'm looking for  Lowrence Nightinggale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.18,0:14:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在后面\N{\fs13}In the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗\N{\fs13}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,玛莎\N{\fs13}Martha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.73,0:14:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,很有可能\N{\fs13}Quite possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.88,0:14:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是这样\N{\fs13}Afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,噢\N{\fs13}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs13}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么事吗\N{\fs13}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs13}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,三十八\N{\fs13}Thirty-eight
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 等一下\N{\fs13}just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 我们见过 是吗\N{\fs13}Hang on. We've met, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你会想起来的\N{\fs13}It'll come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.01,0:14:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 我的老天\N{\fs13}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没错\N{\fs13}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.64,0:14:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 再次抱歉上次…\N{\fs13}Sorry. Sorry, again, about the whole…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你妹妹的消息\N{\fs13}Message from your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:14:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 好的\N{\fs13}Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.53,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她的消息是什么\N{\fs13}What is it? What's the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,她要离开一段时间\N{\fs13}She's had to go away for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪里\N{\fs13}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只是工作上的事 没什么好担心的\N{\fs13}Just a work thing. Nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…\N{\fs13}And…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有什么\N{\fs13}And… And what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她爱你\N{\fs13}She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,她什么\N{\fs13}She what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她是这么说的 她只是顺便提到\N{\fs13}She said to say… She just sort of mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,她爱你 很好 不是吗\N{\fs13}She loves you. There, that's nice, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.30,0:15:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她病了吗\N{\fs13}Is she ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不 没有\N{\fs13}No! No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.45,0:15:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是我病了吗\N{\fs13}Am I ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.98,0:15:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是个恶作剧吗\N{\fs13}Is this a trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.06,0:15:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 她爱你\N{\fs13}No. She loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…人们不理解时间\N{\fs13}People don't understand time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.86,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,它跟你们想的不一样\N{\fs13}It's not what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这个人是谁\N{\fs13}Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 暂停老是失灵\N{\fs13}Sorry, the pause thing keeps slipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.25,0:15:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,蠢东西\N{\fs13}Stupid thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.28,0:15:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚在凯茜家\N{\fs13}Last night at Kathy's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你那些屏幕里也有他 同一个人\N{\fs13}you had him on all those screens, that same guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.53,0:15:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一直在说些什么\N{\fs13}Talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,眨眼之类的东西\N{\fs13}I don't know, blinking or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 眨眼那段不错\N{\fs13}Yeah, the bit about the blinking's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在看它们是不是全都一样\N{\fs13}I was just checking to see if they were all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,什么一样\N{\fs13}What were the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 他是谁\N{\fs13}What is this? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:15:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一个彩蛋\N{\fs13}An Easter egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.75,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs13}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就像DVD花絮 知道吗\N{\fs13}Like a DVD extra, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道在DVD里\N{\fs13}You know how on DVDs
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,会有花絮访谈和幕后片段吧\N{\fs13}they put extras, you know, documentaries and stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.72,0:16:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候这些片段是隐藏起来的\N{\fs13}Sometimes they put on hidden ones
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,他们称之为彩蛋\N{\fs13}and they call them Easter eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你得去找它们\N{\fs13}You have to go looking for them
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.42,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,根据主菜单里的一堆线索\N{\fs13}follow a bunch of clues on the menu screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很复杂\N{\fs13}Complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.50,0:16:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有意思的是\N{\fs13}It's interesting, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他出现在17张不同的DVD上\N{\fs13}He is on 17 different DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,17张完全不相干的DVD上 都有他的片段\N{\fs13}There are 17 totally unrelated DVDs all with him on
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都是隐藏起来的 都是秘密\N{\fs13}always hidden away, always a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至出版商也不知道\N{\fs13}Not even the publishers know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟制片商也谈过 连他们也不知道\N{\fs13}I've talked to the manufacturers, right? They don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他就像是一个鬼魂DVD花絮\N{\fs13}He's like… He's a ghost DVD extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,在他不该出现的地方冒出来\N{\fs13}Just shows up where he's not supposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但只在那些17张DVD上\N{\fs13}But only on those. Those 17.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他在做什么\N{\fs13}Well, what does he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,就坐在那里 说些奇怪的话\N{\fs13}Just sits there, making random remarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.70,0:16:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好像我们在听一段交谈的一半\N{\fs13}It's like we're hearing half a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.41,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我和伙计们一直想找出另外一半\N{\fs13}Me and the guys are always trying to work out the other half.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你和伙计们 你是指网上那些人对吧\N{\fs13}When you say you and the guys, you mean the internet, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道的\N{\fs13}How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真诡异 不是吗\N{\fs13}Spooky, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,非常复杂\N{\fs13}Very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,劳伦斯 来帮忙\N{\fs13}Lawrence, need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉离开一会儿\N{\fs13}Excuse me a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,人们认为时间是严格按照因果顺序进行的\N{\fs13}People assume that time is a strict progression of cause to effect
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实上从非线性 非主观的观点来看\N{\fs13}but actually, from a non-linear, non-subjective viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,时间更像是一大团弯弯绕绕 颠颠倒倒的...东西\N{\fs13}it's more like a big ball of wibbly-wobbly, timey-wimey stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这个句子起得不错\N{\fs13}It started well, that sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.33,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,后面就跑偏了\N{\fs13}It got away from me, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.16,0:17:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这有点诡异\N{\fs13}Okay, that was weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像你能听到我\N{\fs13}Like you can hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我是能听到你\N{\fs13}Well, I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 够了\N{\fs13}Okay, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够了 我今天已经很不顺了\N{\fs13}I've had enough now. I've had a long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的是受够了\N{\fs13}and I've had bloody enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs13}Sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,今天不太顺心\N{\fs13}bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.80,0:17:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,给你找了名单\N{\fs13}Got you the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,那17张DVD 我以为你会感兴趣\N{\fs13}The 17 DVDs. I thought you might be interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对 很好 多谢\N{\fs13}Yeah. Great. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去找警察啊 你这个蠢女人\N{\fs13}Go to the police, you stupid woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么电影里的人总是不找警察\N{\fs13}Why does nobody ever just go to the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我知道这听起来很疯狂\N{\fs13}Look, I know how mad I'm sounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能请你从头开始\N{\fs13}Shall we try it from the beginning this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 有座房子\N{\fs13}Okay, there's this house
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,古老的大房子 空了很多年\N{\fs13}a big, old house, been empty for years
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.47,0:18:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快倒塌了 院子外面写着西丘庄园\N{\fs13}falling apart, Wester Drumlins, out by the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你们也许见过\N{\fs13}You've probably seen it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,西丘庄园\N{\fs13}Wester Drumlins?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.19,0:18:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs13}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里稍等片刻好吗\N{\fs13}Could you just wait here for a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.05,0:19:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我快崩溃了\N{\fs13}Okay. Cracking up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs13}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.66,0:19:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,比利·西普顿警探\N{\fs13}Hi. DI Billy Shipton.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.87,0:19:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,西丘庄园 我的案子\N{\fs13}Wester Drumlins, that's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不能跟你谈 有件要事不能耽误\N{\fs13}Can't talk to you now, got a thing I can't be late for
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以如果你能…\N{\fs13}so if you could just…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs13}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs13}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.40,0:19:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 马西\N{\fs13}Er, Marcie,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.14,0:19:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你能不能告诉他们\N{\fs13}Er, Marcie, can you tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.86,0:19:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我要晚点再处理那件要事\N{\fs13}I'm going to be late for that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是\N{\fs13}All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.16,0:19:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,过去两年里的 没错\N{\fs13}over the last two years, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这些车上都还有私人物品\N{\fs13}They all still have personal items in them
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有些甚至发动机都还开着\N{\fs13}and a couple still had the motor running.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说过去两年里\N{\fs13}So over the last two years
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些车的主人\N{\fs13}the owners of all of these vehicles have driven up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,都开车到了西丘庄园那里\N{\fs13}have driven up to Wester Drumlins house,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.05,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,把车停在外面 然后莫名消失了\N{\fs13}parked outside and just disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么\N{\fs13}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 西丘庄园收藏品中的骄傲\N{\fs13}Ah. The pride of the Wester Drumlins collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,也是在那里发现的\N{\fs13}We found that there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.06,0:19:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜是某人开的玩笑\N{\fs13}Somebody's idea of a joke, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么 警亭是什么\N{\fs13}But what is it? What's a police box?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:20:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是种特殊的警用电话亭\N{\fs13}Well, it's a special kind of phone box for policemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.20,0:20:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,过去到处都有\N{\fs13}They used to have them all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个不是真的\N{\fs13}but this isn't a real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.42,0:20:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,电话是假的 窗户的尺寸也不对\N{\fs13}The phone is just a dummy and the windows are the wrong size.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.67,0:20:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,连门都打不开\N{\fs13}Can't even get in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,很普通的耶鲁锁 但怎么也打不开\N{\fs13}Ordinary Yale lock, but nothing fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但这还不是大问题\N{\fs13}But that's not the big question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 你正在错过大问题\N{\fs13}See, you're missing the big question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.56,0:20:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 什么大问题\N{\fs13}Okay, what's the big question?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以跟我去喝一杯吗\N{\fs13}Will you have a drink with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs13}I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,喝一杯 你和我\N{\fs13}Drink? You, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.38,0:20:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs13}now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是在工作吗\N{\fs13}Aren't you on duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,西普顿警探\N{\fs13}Detective Inspector Shipton?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我早就收工了\N{\fs13}Nope. Knocked off before I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉他们我家里有急事\N{\fs13}Told them I had a family crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs13}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.48,0:20:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,因为生命很短暂 而你又很性感\N{\fs13}Because life is short and you are hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喝一杯\N{\fs13}Drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs13}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,以后呢\N{\fs13}Ever?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.74,0:20:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也许\N{\fs13}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,电话号码\N{\fs13}Phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.58,0:20:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,进展太快了点吧 西普顿警探\N{\fs13}Moving rather fast, DI Shipton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.29,0:20:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我比利 我已经下班了\N{\fs13}Billy. I'm off duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.95,0:20:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\N{\fs13}Aren't you just?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的电话号码\N{\fs13}Is that your phone number?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,只是我的电话号码\N{\fs13}Just my phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不是承诺 不是保证\N{\fs13}Not a promise, not a guarantee,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不是约定 就是个电话号码\N{\fs13}not an IOU, just a phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫莎丽…\N{\fs13}And that's Sally…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽·西普顿\N{\fs13}Sally Shipton
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是斯帕罗\N{\fs13}Sparrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}Sally Sparrow
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了 别看我\N{\fs13}Okay, going now. Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我会打给你 -别看我\N{\fs13}I'll phone you. - Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,明天打给你 -别看我\N{\fs13}Phone you tomorrow. - Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.75,0:21:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也许今晚就打给你\N{\fs13}Might even phone you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,别看我\N{\fs13}Don't look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对会打给你 美女\N{\fs13}Definitely gonna phone you, gorgeous girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.19,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你啦\N{\fs13}Definitely better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很普通的耶鲁锁 但怎么也打不开\N{\fs13}SHIPTON: Ordinary Yale lock, but nothing fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.59,0:23:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你\N{\fs13}DOCTOR: Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.05,0:23:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我在哪里\N{\fs13}Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.34,0:23:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,1969年\N{\fs13}1969.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.90,0:23:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,还不算糟 你可以期待人类登陆月球\N{\fs13}Not bad, as it goes. You've got the moon landing to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.07,0:23:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,登月太好玩了\N{\fs13}Oh, the moon landing's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.78,0:23:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去过四次\N{\fs13}We went four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那时我们的交通工具还在\N{\fs13}Back when we had transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.88,0:23:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,正在想办法\N{\fs13}Working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么到这里来的\N{\fs13}How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.88,0:23:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我们来的方式一样\N{\fs13}Same way we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.07,0:23:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,天使之触\N{\fs13}Touch of an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是同一个 因为你来到同一年\N{\fs13}Same one, probably, since you ended up in the same year.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.36,0:23:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不不 别起来\N{\fs13}No, no, no. Don't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不用时空舱的时间旅行 很危险\N{\fs13}Time travel without a capsule, nasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.22,0:23:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,先喘口气 半小时内别去游泳\N{\fs13}Catch your breath, don't go swimming for half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.62,0:23:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我不游泳 我不会游\N{\fs13}I don't… I can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.37,0:23:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,迷人的种族 哭泣天使\N{\fs13}Fascinating race, the weeping angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙中唯一一种让人善终的疯子\N{\fs13}The only psychopaths in the universe to kill you nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.79,0:23:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,干净利落 不留痕迹\N{\fs13}No mess, no fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.99,0:23:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样把你踢到过去 让你老死\N{\fs13}they just zap you into the past and let you live to death
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.59,0:23:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你的余生在眨眼间就消逝了\N{\fs13}the rest of your life used up and blown away in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.67,0:23:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你在过去死去\N{\fs13}You die in the past
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而它们留在当时吸收\N{\fs13}and in the present they consume
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.85,0:23:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你拥有的时间能量\N{\fs13}the energy of all the days you might have had.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.34,0:23:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,所有被偷走的时间\N{\fs13}All your stolen moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是偷窃的生物 它们靠势能生存\N{\fs13}They're creatures of the abstract, they live off potential energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底在说些什么\N{\fs13}What in God's name are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:24:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,相信我 当他停下喘口气时你点头就是了\N{\fs13}Trust me, just nod when he stops for breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个找到你的\N{\fs13}Tracked you down with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这个是我的"时间错乱"探测器\N{\fs13}This is my timey-wimey detector.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.61,0:24:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,发现异常它就会发出"叮"的声音\N{\fs13}lso, it can boil an egg at 30 paces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也能使30步以内的鸡蛋煮熟\N{\fs13}Also, it can boil an egg at 30 paces.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.92,0:24:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,而且根本控制不住\N{\fs13}Whether you want it to or not, actually
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我已学会远离母鸡了\N{\fs13}so I've learnt to stay away from hens.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.58,0:24:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,母鸡爆炸可不太好看\N{\fs13}It's not pretty when they blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.74,0:24:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白 我在哪里\N{\fs13}I don't understand. Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.31,0:24:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,1969年 如他所说\N{\fs13}1969, like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.55,0:24:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,通常我会载你回家\N{\fs13}Normally, I'd offer you a lift home,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不过这次我的车被偷了\N{\fs13}but somebody nicked my motor.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我需要你带个话给莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}So I need you to take a message to Sally Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.01,0:24:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 比利\N{\fs13}And I'm sorry, Billy,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.84,0:24:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的真的很抱歉\N{\fs13}I am very, very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.05,0:24:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这得耗费你很长一段时间\N{\fs13}It's gonna take you a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.72,0:24:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喂\N{\fs13}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.51,0:24:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,比利 你在哪里\N{\fs13}Billy, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.06,0:24:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.96,0:25:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,比利\N{\fs13}Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.52,0:25:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们见面那天也在下雨\N{\fs13}It was raining when we met.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.27,0:25:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是刚刚那场雨\N{\fs13}It's the same rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.37,0:25:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她看起来不错\N{\fs13}She looks nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.57,0:25:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她也叫莎丽\N{\fs13}Her name was Sally, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.96,0:25:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽·西普顿\N{\fs13}Sally Shipton.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.84,0:25:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽·西普顿\N{\fs13}Sally Shipton!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.80,0:25:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我经常想着早一点来找你\N{\fs13}I often thought about looking for you before tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.18,0:26:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然那会在时空结构上捅出一个大洞\N{\fs13}But apparently it would have torn a hole in the fabric of space and time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.41,0:26:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,并且摧毁宇宙的三分之二\N{\fs13}and destroyed two thirds of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.05,0:26:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,而且\N{\fs13}Also,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.19,0:26:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还会使我秃顶\N{\fs13}I'd lost my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.39,0:26:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙的三分之二 谁告诉你的\N{\fs13}Two thirds of the universe? Where'd you get that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.38,0:26:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,有个人在1969年 叫我给你带个话\N{\fs13}There's a man in 1969. He sent me with a message for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.02,0:26:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么人\N{\fs13}What man?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs13}The Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.70,0:26:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,带的话是什么\N{\fs13}And what was the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.17,0:26:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这个\N{\fs13}just this
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.80,0:26:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"看看名单"\N{\fs13}"look at the list".
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.42,0:26:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么意思\N{\fs13}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.57,0:26:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这点 "看看名单"\N{\fs13}Is that it? Look at the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.93,0:26:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他说你现在应该有名单了\N{\fs13}He said you'd have it by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.77,0:26:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,17张DVD的名单\N{\fs13}A list of 17 DVDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.44,0:26:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我在过去并没做警察\N{\fs13}I didn't stay a policeman back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.60,0:26:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,而是从事了出版业\N{\fs13}Got into publishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.66,0:26:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,然后是视频出版\N{\fs13}then video publishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.86,0:26:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,然后…当然是DVD出版\N{\fs13}Then DVDs, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.02,0:26:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是你把彩蛋加进去的\N{\fs13}You put the Easter egg on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.63,0:26:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你注意到那17张DVD的共同点了吗\N{\fs13}Have you noticed what all 17 DVDs have in common yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.20,0:27:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜那对你有点难\N{\fs13}I suppose it's hard for you in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.87,0:27:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,博士怎么知道我有名单\N{\fs13}How could the Doctor have even known I had a list?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.29,0:27:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我才刚刚拿到\N{\fs13}I only just got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.67,0:27:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我问过他\N{\fs13}I asked him how
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.58,0:27:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但他说 他没办法告诉我\N{\fs13}but he said he couldn't tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.97,0:27:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他说有一天你会明白的\N{\fs13}He said you'd understand it one day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.67,0:27:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但我…永远不能\N{\fs13}but that I never would.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.46,0:27:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我一明白就回来告诉你\N{\fs13}Soon as I understand it, I'll come and tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.96,0:27:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了 美女\N{\fs13}No, gorgeous girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.10,0:27:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能\N{\fs13}You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.74,0:27:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我只剩下今晚了\N{\fs13}There's only tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.54,0:27:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,多年前他告诉我\N{\fs13}He told me all those years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.40,0:27:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会再次相遇\N{\fs13}that we'll only meet again
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.71,0:27:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只能是这一次\N{\fs13}this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.88,0:27:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在我死去的那个晚上\N{\fs13}On the night I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.12,0:27:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 比利\N{\fs13}Oh, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.82,0:27:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这一直支撑着我\N{\fs13}It's kept me going.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.28,0:27:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在又老又病\N{\fs13}I'm an old, sick man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.24,0:27:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有一件事值得我去期待\N{\fs13}But I've had something to look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.93,0:27:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,生命如此漫长 你却美丽依然\N{\fs13}Ah, life is long and you are hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看看我的手\N{\fs13}Look at my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.77,0:28:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这双老人的手\N{\fs13}An old man's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.01,0:28:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么发生的\N{\fs13}How did that happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.77,0:28:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我会留在这儿\N{\fs13}I'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.15,0:28:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我留下来陪你 好吗\N{\fs13}I'm gonna stay with you, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.06,0:28:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}Thank you, Sally Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.93,0:28:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雨停之后就是我的尽头\N{\fs13}I have till the rain stops.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.86,0:28:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Banto小店\N{\fs13}Bantos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.83,0:28:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是我的\N{\fs13}They're mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.88,0:28:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.91,0:29:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,名单上的17张DVD\N{\fs13}The DVDs on the list, the 17 DVDs,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.46,0:29:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的共同点就是我\N{\fs13}what they've got in common is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.26,0:29:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这些DVD都属于我\N{\fs13}They're all the DVDs I own.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.65,0:29:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那个彩蛋是设计来给我的\N{\fs13}The Easter egg was intended for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.50,0:29:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,总共只有17张DVD吗\N{\fs13}You've only got 17 DVDs?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.62,0:29:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有便携式DVD播放机\N{\fs13}Do you have a portable DVD player?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.09,0:29:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有 怎么了\N{\fs13}Of course. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.08,0:29:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你跟我碰面\N{\fs13}I want you to meet me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.76,0:29:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里\N{\fs13}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.85,0:29:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,西丘庄园\N{\fs13}Wester Drumlin
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.71,0:29:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道你家会像史酷比家一样阴森\N{\fs13}I knew you would live in Scooby Doo's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.34,0:29:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托 我不住在这里\N{\fs13}For God's sake, I don't live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.91,0:29:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这张是声音最清晰的\N{\fs13}This is the one with the clearest sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.52,0:29:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这张画质更好一点\N{\fs13}Slightly better picture quality on this one
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.44,0:29:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道… -无关紧要\N{\fs13}but I don't know… - Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.65,0:29:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs13}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.32,0:29:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他出来了\N{\fs13}There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.05,0:29:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs13}The Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.64,0:29:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,博士是谁\N{\fs13}Who's a doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.84,0:29:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是博士\N{\fs13}He's the Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.95,0:29:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就是我\N{\fs13}Yup, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.74,0:30:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这挺吓人的\N{\fs13}Okay, that was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.27,0:30:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不 听起来像是他在回答你\N{\fs13}No, it sounds like he's replying
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.54,0:30:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,但他每次都是这么说的\N{\fs13}but he always says that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 没错\N{\fs13}Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.57,0:30:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,还有这句\N{\fs13}And that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.34,0:30:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 这句也是\N{\fs13}Yup. And this.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.47,0:30:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他能听见我们\N{\fs13}He can hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.35,0:30:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 你真的能听见我们\N{\fs13}Oh, my God. You can really hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.08,0:30:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他当然听不见我们\N{\fs13}Of course he can't hear us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.52,0:30:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看\N{\fs13}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.47,0:30:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我有抄本 瞧\N{\fs13}I've got a transcript, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.94,0:30:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的每句话\N{\fs13}Everything he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.33,0:30:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,"没错 就是我" "是的 没错"\N{\fs13}"Yup, that's me." "Yes, I do."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.30,0:30:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,"是的 这句也是" 下一句是…\N{\fs13}"Yup, and this." Next, it's…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.83,0:30:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算读完一整篇\N{\fs13}BOTH: Are you gonna read out the whole thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.99,0:30:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.16,0:30:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fs13}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.66,0:30:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个时间旅行者\N{\fs13}I'm a time traveller.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.47,0:30:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,或者说曾经是\N{\fs13}or! I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.50,0:30:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我被困在1969年了\N{\fs13}I'm stuck in 1969.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.41,0:30:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,"我们"被困住了\N{\fs13}We 're stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.61,0:30:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他答应过带我到所有时间和空间\N{\fs13}All of space and time, he promised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.18,0:30:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我却要在店里工作来养活他\N{\fs13}Now I've got a job in a shop. I've gotta support him!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.13,0:30:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,玛莎\N{\fs13}Martha!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.38,0:30:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs13}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.36,0:30:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这段我以前看过\N{\fs13}I've seen this bit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.10,0:30:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,很有可能\N{\fs13}Quite possibly.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.11,0:30:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,1969年 你是在那里说话吗\N{\fs13}1969, that's where you're talking from?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.23,0:30:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是的\N{\fs13}Afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.96,0:30:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但你在回答我\N{\fs13}But you're replying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.09,0:30:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不可能知道我会说什么\N{\fs13}You can't know exactly what I'm gonna say
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.85,0:30:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在我说之前40年\N{\fs13}40 years before I say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.72,0:30:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,38年\N{\fs13}38.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.82,0:30:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把这些写下来 我要把你的话写下来\N{\fs13}I'm getting this down. I'm writing in your bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.08,0:30:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的\N{\fs13}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.77,0:30:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这怎么可能 告诉我\N{\fs13}How is this possible? Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.72,0:30:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么快\N{\fs13}Not so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.65,0:31:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,人们不了解时间 它不是你们想像的那样子\N{\fs13}People don't understand time. It's not what you think it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.53,0:31:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那它是什么样的\N{\fs13}Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.90,0:31:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,很复杂\N{\fs13}Complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.89,0:31:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fs13}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.46,0:31:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,非常复杂\N{\fs13}Very complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.47,0:31:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我很聪明 我在听着\N{\fs13}I'm clever and I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.96,0:31:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,别故作高深了 因为已经有人死了\N{\fs13}And don't patronise me because people have died
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.13,0:31:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,而我并不高兴\N{\fs13}and I'm not happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.67,0:31:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我\N{\fs13}Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.41,0:31:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,人们假定时间是严格按照因果顺序进行的\N{\fs13}People assume that time is a strict progression of cause to effect
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.04,0:31:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但事实上从非线性 非主观的观点来看\N{\fs13}but actually, from a non-linear, non-subjective viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.98,0:31:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,时间更像是一个弯弯曲曲变化无常的大球\N{\fs13}it's more like a big ball of wibbly-wobbly, timey-wimey stuffi.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.36,0:31:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我以前看到过这段\N{\fs13}Yeah, I've seen this bit before.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.87,0:31:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你说那句话是你脱口而出的\N{\fs13}You said that sentence got away from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.77,0:31:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,脱口而出了 是啊\N{\fs13}It got away from me, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.60,0:31:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,下一句你要说的是 "是啊 我能听到你"\N{\fs13}Next thing you're gonna say is, "Well, I can hear you."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.81,0:31:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 我能听到你\N{\fs13}Well, I can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.93,0:31:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fs13}This is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.18,0:31:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 太赞了\N{\fs13}No. It's brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.41,0:31:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其实不是真的能听见你\N{\fs13}Well, not hear you, exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.74,0:31:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我知道你要说的每一句话\N{\fs13}but I know everything you're gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.86,0:31:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这句总是让我毛骨悚然\N{\fs13}Always gives me the shivers, that bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.00,0:31:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能知道我要说什么\N{\fs13}How can you know what I'm gonna say?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.88,0:31:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的左边\N{\fs13}Look to your left.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.08,0:31:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他说"看你的左边"是什么意思\N{\fs13}What's he mean by "look to your left"?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.93,0:31:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我在论坛上写了一大堆\N{\fs13}I've written tons about that in the forums.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.42,0:31:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为那是个政治术语\N{\fs13}I think it's a political statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.86,0:32:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他说的是你 你在干什么\N{\fs13}He means you. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.08,0:32:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,记录你说的话\N{\fs13}I'm writing in your bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.23,0:32:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这样我就得到了一份这段对话的完整抄本\N{\fs13}That way, I've got a complete transcript of the whole conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.52,0:32:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,等到这个发到网上\N{\fs13}Wait until this hits the Net.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.90,0:32:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,一定会在彩蛋论坛引起轰动\N{\fs13}This will explode the egg forums.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.84,0:32:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经拿到一份完成的抄本\N{\fs13}I've got a copy of the finished transcript,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.47,0:32:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就在我的提词机上\N{\fs13}it's on my Autocue.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.61,0:32:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能得到一份已完成的抄本\N{\fs13}How can you have a copy of the finished transcript?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.34,0:32:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,他还在写呢\N{\fs13}It's still being written.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.86,0:32:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了 我是个时间旅行者 我从未来拿的\N{\fs13}I told you, I'm a time traveller. I got it in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.52,0:32:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 让我梳理一下头绪\N{\fs13}Okay, let me get my head round this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.48,0:32:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在读一份你正在进行的对话的抄本\N{\fs13}You're reading aloud from a transcript of a conversation you're still having.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.46,0:32:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,呃…时间弯弯曲曲变化无常\N{\fs13}Wibbly-wobbly, timey-wimey…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.37,0:32:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,现在别管那个了 你会速记\N{\fs13}Actually, never mind that. You can do shorthand?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.52,0:32:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样\N{\fs13}So?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.90,0:32:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,重要的是我们能沟通\N{\fs13}What matters is we can communicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.36,0:32:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在有个大麻烦\N{\fs13}We have got big problems now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.98,0:32:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,它们带走了蓝盒子 对不对\N{\fs13}They have taken the blue box, haven 't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.21,0:32:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天使们偷走了蓝盒子\N{\fs13}The angels have the phone box?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.22,0:32:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"天使们偷走了蓝盒子" 我最喜欢的一句\N{\fs13}"The angels have the phone box", that's my favourite.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.51,0:32:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要印在T恤上\N{\fs13}I've got that on a T-shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.25,0:32:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的天使是什么意思\N{\fs13}What do you mean, angels?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.14,0:32:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说那些雕像\N{\fs13}You mean those statue things?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.53,0:32:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,来自另一个世界的生物\N{\fs13}Creatures from another world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.70,0:32:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但它们只是雕像啊\N{\fs13}But they're just statues.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.82,0:32:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,只有在你看见的时候是\N{\fs13}only when you see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.52,0:32:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fs13}What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.49,0:33:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,它们曾被称为"孤独的刺客"\N{\fs13}The Lonely Assassins they used to be called.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.03,0:33:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没人清楚它们来自哪里\N{\fs13}No one quite knows where they came from
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.34,0:33:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,它们跟宇宙一样古老\N{\fs13}but they're as old as the universe
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.82,0:33:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,或者差不多 它们能活那么长是因为\N{\fs13}or very nearly, and they have survived this long
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.85,0:33:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,它们拥有最完美的防御系统\N{\fs13}because they have the most perfect defence system ever evolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.34,0:33:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,它们是量子锁定的\N{\fs13}They are quantum locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.81,0:33:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,当被观察时它们并不存在\N{\fs13}They don't exist when they're being observed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.80,0:33:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,它们被任何生物看到时\N{\fs13}The moment they are seen by any other living creature
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.01,0:33:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,都会化为石头\N{\fs13}they freeze into rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.91,0:33:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那是它们的生物特性\N{\fs13}No choice, it's a fact of their biology.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.60,0:33:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在任何生物的视线里\N{\fs13}In the sight of any living thing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.60,0:33:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,它们完全变成石头\N{\fs13}they literally turn to stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.97,0:33:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你没法杀死石头\N{\fs13}And you can't kill a stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.67,0:33:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 石头也不会来杀你\N{\fs13}Course, a stone can't kill you, either
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.33,0:33:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 一旦你转移视线\N{\fs13}but then you turn your head away.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.34,0:33:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你一眨眼\N{\fs13}Then you blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.16,0:33:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这时 没错 它就能杀你\N{\fs13}And, oh, yes, it can.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.60,0:33:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不要移开你的视线\N{\fs13}Don't take your eyes off that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.12,0:33:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是它们蒙上自己双眼的原因\N{\fs13}That'.s why they cover their eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.76,0:33:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,它们不是在哭泣 而是不能冒险看到对方\N{\fs13}They're not weeping, they can't risk looking at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.46,0:33:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,它们最强大的武器 也是它们最大的诅咒\N{\fs13}Their greatest asset is their greatest curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.39,0:33:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,它们永远都无法被看到\N{\fs13}They can never be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.03,0:33:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙中最孤独的生物\N{\fs13}Loneliest creatures in the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.90,0:33:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 非常非常抱歉\N{\fs13}Well, I'm sorry. I am very, very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.29,0:33:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在全靠你自己了\N{\fs13}It's up to you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.28,0:33:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该怎么做\N{\fs13}What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.64,0:33:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那个蓝盒子 是我的时间机器\N{\fs13}The blue box. It's my time machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.30,0:33:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那里拥有足够它们永久享用的巨大能量\N{\fs13}There is a world of time energy in there they could feast on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.27,0:34:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也有可能产生毁天灭地的破坏力\N{\fs13}but the damage they could do could switch off the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.35,0:34:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须把它送来给我\N{\fs13}You have got to send it back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.45,0:34:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么送\N{\fs13}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.87,0:34:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么送\N{\fs13}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.42,0:34:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕到头了\N{\fs13}And that's it, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.24,0:34:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,抄本里没有下文了\N{\fs13}There's no more from you on the transcript,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.08,0:34:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只有这些\N{\fs13}that's the last I've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.52,0:34:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我不清楚是什么让你停止谈话\N{\fs13}I don't know what stopped you talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.86,0:34:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但我猜是它们来了\N{\fs13}but I can guess. They're coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.51,0:34:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,天使来找你们了\N{\fs13}The angels are coming for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.95,0:34:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,听好\N{\fs13}But listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.21,0:34:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你的性命可能全靠这个了\N{\fs13}your life could depend on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.53,0:34:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,别眨眼 一下都不能眨 一眨眼你就会死\N{\fs13}Don't blink. Don't even blink. Blink and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.40,0:34:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,它们很快 快的超出你的想像\N{\fs13}They are fast. Faster than you can believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.47,0:34:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,别转身 别回头 千万别眨眼\N{\fs13}Don't turn your back, don't look away and don't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.60,0:34:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs13}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不要 你不能\N{\fs13}No, don't. You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.13,0:34:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我把它倒回去\N{\fs13}I'll rewind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.05,0:34:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,倒回去有什么用\N{\fs13}What good will that do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.66,0:34:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有在盯着雕像\N{\fs13}You're not looking at the statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.24,0:34:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你也没有\N{\fs13}Neither are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.17,0:34:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,盯着它\N{\fs13}Looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.48,0:34:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,一直盯着它\N{\fs13}Keep looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.90,0:34:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一个 对吧\N{\fs13}It's just one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.30,0:34:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这一个\N{\fs13}It's just this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.14,0:35:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一直盯着这个雕像\N{\fs13}We're okay if we just keep staring at this one statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.72,0:35:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们就会没事\N{\fs13}Everything's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.92,0:35:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,还有三个\N{\fs13}There's three more.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.85,0:35:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,三个\N{\fs13}Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,它们之前在楼上\N{\fs13}They were upstairs before
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.93,0:35:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但我好像听到它们动了\N{\fs13}but I think I heard them moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.24,0:35:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在哪里 三个 往哪里移动\N{\fs13}Moving? Three of them? Moving where?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.13,0:35:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我去四处看看 检查一下\N{\fs13}I'm gonna look around. I'm gonna check.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.93,0:35:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直盯着这个 别眨眼\N{\fs13}You keep looking at this one. Don't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.49,0:35:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,记住他说的 千万别眨眼\N{\fs13}Remember what he said. Don't even blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.49,0:35:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会眨眼 我害怕得眨不了眼了\N{\fs13}Who blinked? I'm too scared to blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.74,0:35:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们要去门口 前门\N{\fs13}Okay, we're going to the door. Front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.49,0:35:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们不能两个都去门口\N{\fs13}Okay, we can't both get to the front door
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.03,0:35:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就没人盯着那个东西 你留在这里\N{\fs13}without taking our eyes off that thing, so you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.53,0:35:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.11,0:35:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在附近 你待在这里\N{\fs13}I'll be just round the corner. You stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.34,0:35:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它们把门锁住了 它们把我们锁在里面了\N{\fs13}They've locked it! They've locked us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.69,0:35:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs13}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.96,0:35:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我有它们想要的东西\N{\fs13}I've got something they want.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.27,0:35:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs13}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.11,0:35:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那把钥匙\N{\fs13}The key.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.84,0:35:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我上次来这里拿到的\N{\fs13}I took it last time I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.06,0:35:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它们跟着我就是想拿回去\N{\fs13}They followed me to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.63,0:35:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我带它们去到了蓝盒子那里\N{\fs13}I led them to the blue box.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.78,0:35:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,现在它们有了蓝盒子\N{\fs13}Now they've got that.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.13,0:35:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,把钥匙给它们吧\N{\fs13}Give them the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.77,0:35:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我去看看后门 你在这里等着\N{\fs13}I'm gonna check the back door. You wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.05,0:35:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把钥匙给它们 它们想要就给它们吧\N{\fs13}Give them the key! Give them what they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.34,0:36:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 不要 它们从后面过来怎么办\N{\fs13}Sally, no! What if they come behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.48,0:36:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,坚持住\N{\fs13}Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.69,0:36:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\fs13}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.66,0:36:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天呐\N{\fs13}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.35,0:36:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,锁住了\N{\fs13}It's locked!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.00,0:36:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 莎丽\N{\fs13}Sally! Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.72,0:36:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,打不开\N{\fs13}It won't open!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.23,0:36:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 求你 我不行了\N{\fs13}Sally, please, I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.52,0:36:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 快点\N{\fs13}Sally, hurry UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.67,0:36:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哪里\N{\fs13}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.42,0:36:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,拉瑞\N{\fs13}Larry,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.05,0:36:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它们锁住了后门 但这儿有个地下室\N{\fs13}they've blocked up the back door, but there's a cellar.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.56,0:36:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那里也许有出路 送货口之类的\N{\fs13}There might be a way out. Delivery hatch or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.31,0:36:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了\N{\fs13}I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.40,0:36:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我待不下去了\N{\fs13}I can't stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.14,0:37:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 伙计们\N{\fs13}Okay, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.62,0:37:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们知道原理\N{\fs13}We know how this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.30,0:37:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我看着你们 你们就动不了\N{\fs13}You can't move so long as I can see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.88,0:37:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,博士说 亭子里有一整个世界\N{\fs13}A whole world in the box, the Doctor says.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.71,0:37:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,希望他没说谎\N{\fs13}I hope he's not lying
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.73,0:37:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看不出哪里还有别的出路\N{\fs13}'cause I don't see how else we're getting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.05,0:37:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 你那个也来了\N{\fs13}Oh, and there's your one.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.26,0:37:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,它为什么指向…\N{\fs13}Why is it pointing at the…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.02,0:37:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,灯\N{\fs13}light?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.02,0:37:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 它要关灯\N{\fs13}Oh, my God, it's turning out the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.38,0:37:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,快点\N{\fs13}Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.06,0:38:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我找不到门锁\N{\fs13} I can't find the lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.82,0:38:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 快点\N{\fs13}Sally, hurry UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.59,0:38:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,快打开\N{\fs13}Get it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.20,0:38:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,它们越来越快了 莎丽 快点\N{\fs13}They're getting faster, Sally! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.16,0:38:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,转不动\N{\fs13}It won't turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.20,0:38:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,转不了\N{\fs13}I can't turn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.72,0:38:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽\N{\fs13}Sally!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.06,0:38:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽 赶快\N{\fs13}Sally, hurry up! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.31,0:38:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这是安全协议第712号\N{\fs13}DOCTOR: This is Security Protocol 712.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.68,0:38:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个时空舱探测到已授权的控制碟的存在\N{\fs13}This time capsule has detected the presence of an authorised control disc
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.21,0:38:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,授权一次旅行机会\N{\fs13}valid one journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.11,0:38:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,请插入碟片并准备起飞\N{\fs13}Please insert the disc and prepare for departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.03,0:38:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去像DVD播放器 有个插槽\N{\fs13}Looks like a DVD player. There's a slot.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.33,0:38:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它们想闯进来\N{\fs13}They're trying to get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.56,0:38:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,那你快点啊\N{\fs13}Well, hurry up, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.95,0:39:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事\N{\fs13}What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.00,0:39:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 它要把我们留在这儿\N{\fs13}Oh, my God, it's leaving us behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.00,0:39:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 不要 你不能\N{\fs13}Doctor, don't! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.80,0:39:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs13}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.38,0:39:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,盯着它们 快 盯着它们\N{\fs13}Look at them! Quick, look at them!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.68,0:39:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们不需要了\N{\fs13}I don't think we need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.72,0:40:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他耍了它们 博士耍了它们\N{\fs13}He tricked them. The Doctor tricked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.07,0:40:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,它们在互相看着对方\N{\fs13}They're looking at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.68,0:40:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,它们再也动不了了\N{\fs13}They're never gonna move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.23,0:40:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\fn黑体\\bord0\b1\fs23\shad2}一 年 之 后
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.09,0:40:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你能照看一下店铺吗 我去隔壁买点牛奶\N{\fs13}Can you mind the shop? I'm just nipping next door for some milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.59,0:40:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 不用担心\N{\fs13}Yeah, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.62,0:40:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fs13}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.86,0:40:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fs13}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.32,0:40:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽\N{\fs13}Sally.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.57,0:40:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不能放手吗\N{\fs13}Can't you let it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.09,0:40:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然没办法放手\N{\fs13}Of course I can't let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.50,0:40:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都过去了\N{\fs13}This is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.86,0:41:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,博士要怎么知道去哪里的墙上写那些话\N{\fs13}How did the Doctor know where to write those words on the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.45,0:41:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他怎么得到抄本的\N{\fs13}How could he get a copy of the transcript?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.28,0:41:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,他是从哪里得到那些信息的\N{\fs13}Where did he get all that information from?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.33,0:41:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 有些事情你永远无法弄明白 但那没关系\N{\fs13}Look, some things you never find out and that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.30,0:41:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不 有关系\N{\fs13}No, it isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.80,0:41:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有没有想过这会阻碍一些\N{\fs13}Ever think this might be getting in the way of
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.09,0:41:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,其他事情\N{\fs13}other things?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.85,0:41:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是一起开店\N{\fs13}We just run a shop together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.82,0:41:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,仅此而已 只是开店\N{\fs13}That's all it is, just a shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.76,0:41:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,总之…\N{\fs13}Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.26,0:41:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,牛奶\N{\fs13}Milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.59,0:41:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿就回来\N{\fs13}Back in a mo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 肯定是这条路\N{\fs13}Right, it's definitely this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.80,0:42:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 博士 博士\N{\fs13}Doctor! Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.10,0:42:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 对不起 有点急事\N{\fs13}Hello. Sorry, bit of a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.80,0:42:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有件很重要的事我们得去阻止\N{\fs13}There's a sort of thing happening. Very important that we stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.86,0:42:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 是你\N{\fs13}Oh, my God, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.58,0:42:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是你\N{\fs13}It really is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.62,0:42:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你不记得我了吗\N{\fs13}Oh, you don't remember me, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.29,0:42:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,博士 我们没时间耽误了 迁移已经开始了\N{\fs13}Doctor, we haven't got time for this. Migration's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 很抱歉 我的生活有点复杂\N{\fs13}Look, sorry, I've got a bit of a complex life.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.37,0:42:17.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我身上发生的事情总是不按顺序来的\N{\fs13}Things don't always happen to me in quite the right order.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.82,0:42:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,经常搞得我很困惑\N{\fs13}Gets a bit confusing at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.37,0:42:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是结婚 我对结婚很不在行\N{\fs13}especially at weddings. I'm rubbish at weddings,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.49,0:42:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是我自己的\N{\fs13}Iespecially my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.76,0:42:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 对啊\N{\fs13}Oh, my God, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.67,0:42:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个时间旅行者\N{\fs13}You're a time traveller.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.44,0:42:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那些事还没发生在你身上 全都没有\N{\fs13}It hasn't happened to you yet, none of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.14,0:42:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还在你的未来\N{\fs13}It's still in your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.62,0:42:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么还没发生\N{\fs13}What hasn't happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.35,0:42:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,博士快点 还有20分钟到警戒线\N{\fs13}Doctor, please! 20 minutes to hatching.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.30,0:42:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\N{\fs13}It was me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.38,0:42:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,天呐 从一开始就是我\N{\fs13}Oh, for God's sake, it was me all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.33,0:42:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是从我这里得到的\N{\fs13}You got it all from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.96,0:42:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,得到什么\N{\fs13}Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.10,0:42:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 听着\N{\fs13}Okay, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,有一天你会被困在1969年\N{\fs13}One day, you're gonna get stuck in 1969.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.06,0:42:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,确保把这个带在你身边\N{\fs13}Make sure you've got this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.97,0:42:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你会需要它的\N{\fs13}You're gonna need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.68,0:42:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs13}Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.44,0:42:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 听着 我得赶紧了\N{\fs13}Yeah! Listen, listen, gotta dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.21,0:42:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,有大事发生\N{\fs13}Things happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.23,0:42:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,其实是四件事\N{\fs13}Well, four things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.45,0:42:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 四件事还有一只蜥蜴\N{\fs13}Well, four things and a lizard.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.78,0:42:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 别担心\N{\fs13}Okay, no worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.53,0:42:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你去吧 某天再见\N{\fs13}On you go. See you around some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.82,0:42:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\fs13}What was your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.93,0:43:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}Sally Sparrow
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.12,0:43:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你 莎丽·斯帕罗\N{\fs13}Good to meet you, Sally Sparrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.34,0:43:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 博士\N{\fs13}Goodbye, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.84,0:43:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnSimHei\fs20\1c&F7F7F7\3c&B37329\bord2\\an8}麻雀和夜莺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H202020\bord1}古籍和稀有DVD商店
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.96,0:43:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别眨眼\N{\fs13}Don't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.36,0:43:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,一眨眼你就会死\N{\fs13}Blink and you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.39,0:43:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,别转身\N{\fs13}Don't turn your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.85,0:43:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,别回头\N{\fs13}Don't look away.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.02,0:43:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,千万别眨眼\N{\fs13}And don't blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.38,0:44:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运\N{\fs13}Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.02,0:44:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要去宇宙的尽头\N{\fs13}We're going to the end of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.30,0:44:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(500,500)\pos(172,185}{\fnSimHei\fs28\bord0\b1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}下集预告
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.81,0:44:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,呼唤穿越星际而来 一遍又一遍\N{\fs13}The call came from across the stars, over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.06,0:44:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"来到乌托邦"\N{\fs13}"Come to Utopia."
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.44,0:44:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,博士\N{\fs13}Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.66,0:44:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,上校\N{\fs13}Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.41,0:44:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是未来族\N{\fs13}It's a future time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.60,0:44:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,乌托邦是什么\N{\fs13}Utopia is…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.66,0:44:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一批人类在晚上散开了\N{\fs13}The last of the humans, scattered across the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.92,0:44:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,人类要来了\N{\fs13}Humans are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.73,0:44:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,即使时间领主也不该走到这么远\N{\fs13}Not even us Time Lords came this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.04,0:44:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该走了\N{\fs13}We should leave.
